Joe Correnti
Senior Vice President, Brokerage Products
Scottrade, Inc.

Joe Correnti is the senior vice president of Brokerage Products at Scottrade, Inc. In his role, Joe oversees the strategy and development of products and solutions that help Scottrade’s clients make better investing decisions and react quickly to trading opportunities.








Joe’s primary focus is to ensure that self-directed traders and long-term investors interested in seeking additional guidance have access to the products and services to empower them. With more than 15 years of experience, his expertise includes insight on products, solutions and investment strategies designed to help investors reach their financial goals.



































